{"tid":471595,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蠔涌炸彈案】兩人無罪、三人罪成即時還押等候量刑","createTime":"2017-11-17T11:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T13:06:30.000Z","uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c25ee7888f09f0da5dd029d5e701dd682931908b","tid":471595,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:53:13.000Z","msg":"【蠔涌案】陪審團裁定三人罪成、兩人無罪｜三人即時還柙等候量刑<br />\n<br />\n前年西貢蠔涌亞視(ATV)舊片廠懷疑爆炸品案，五人被控串謀製造炸藥罪及管有炸藥共五項罪名，案件今日（十七日）在高等法院宣判，陪審團經一日半退庭商議，裁定三人罪成，兩人無罪釋放。<br />\n<br />\n本案第一被告陳耀成、第二被告鄭偉成、第三被告彭艾烈、第四被告胡啟賦及第五被告文廷洛皆被控串謀製造爆炸品(Conspiracy to make explosives)，其中第二及第三被告罪成，第一、第四及第五被告無罪。第一至第三被告另被控管有爆炸品罪成。<br />\n<br />\n本土新聞"},{"pid":"51028ec30c099c89d11a3d98bb6ff8b34f245309","tid":471595,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:34:02.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e742abb0e0308653fb82fd067eed187067a3b66f","tid":471595,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:45:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb30716fc53f59a2a93970b42e5b3b313f07f3cf","tid":471595,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:58:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a16760ce7c0cdf32381330c0b7cbd98c8c49d7d","tid":471595,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:00:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>散播失敗主義梗係冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係散播失敗主義，係直情失敗左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b01d4def4dc27f902a4e62167d0a5c261e90fb","tid":471595,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:06:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}